    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-08-03T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-08-03T04:00:00-05:00" n="74"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d74">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111N39/4</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Norway</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SAG1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schmedeman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="italic">Christiania</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-03T10:00:00+01:00">
                        <hi rend="italic">August 3, 1914, 10 a.m.</hi>
                    </date>
                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 10:15 a.m.</hi>] </dateline>
                <p rend="center">[Telegram]</p>
                <p>On August 1 Norwegian Cabinet issued a proclamation that Norway will maintain
                    strict neutrality in war between Austria-Hungary and Servia. Yesterday morning
                    Cabinet issued an order to mobilize <pb facs="0349" n="35" xml:id="pg_35"/> at
                    once the entire navy and two brigades for coast defense. Export of grain and
                    flour, potatoes, coal, coke and mineral oils temporarily prohibited. Storthing
                    has been called for August 8.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_SAG1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Schmedeman</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
